{"ja242:0.1":"Jataka ","ja242:0.2":"Dukanipata ","ja242:0.3":"Singalavagga ","ja242:0.4":"2. Sunakhajataka ","ja242:1.1":"“Balo vatayam sunakho, ","ja242:1.2":"yo varattam na khadati; ","ja242:1.3":"Bandhana ca pamunceyya, ","ja242:1.4":"asito ca gharam vaje”. ","ja242:2.1":"“Atthitam me manasmim me, ","ja242:2.2":"atho me hadaye katam; ","ja242:2.3":"Kalanca patikankhami, ","ja242:2.4":"yava passupatu jano”ti. ","ja242:3.1":"Sunakhajatakam dutiyam. "}